July 28, 2017 11:32 PM ET
Trading Companies and Distributors

Company Overview of Vis Vires Group, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Vis Vires Group, Inc. is a debt issuing vehicle. The company is based in Great Neck, New York. Vis Vires Group, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Nishiyama Corp.


111 Great Neck RoadSuite 216Great Neck, NY 11021United States










Key Executives for Vis Vires Group, Inc.




Mr. Curt Kramer


      	President
      





Compensation as of Fiscal Year 2017. 

Vis Vires Group, Inc. Key Developments

Players Network Files a Complaint Against Vis Vires Group, KBM Worldwide, Inc. and Asher Enterprises
Nov 9 15
Players Network, Inc. announced that it has filed a lawsuit in the district Court of Clark County, Nevada, against Vis Vires Group Inc., KBM Worldwide Inc., Asher Enterprises Inc., and Seth Kramer and Curt Kramer, individually. The case is currently contested by the defendants in both Federal and State Courts in New York and Nevada. In this case Players Network is suing for an undisclosed amount for injunctive relief, actual damages and punitive damages. The suit was filed on behalf of PNTV by Bloom Donohue Young LLP.


